            <h1>
	  			<div class="tweet-btn">
					<iframe allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" src="/a/1314118012/iframe/tweet_button.html#en" style="height: 20px; width: 55px; "></iframe>
				</div>
				Promoted Trends
			</h1>
              <p class="lead">Use Promoted Trends to drive conversations and interest around your brand or product by capturing a user’s attention on Twitter.</p>
<p>Every minute of every day, Twitter hosts viral conversations that reflect some of the hottest topics of the moment. These trends are featured prominently next to a user’s timeline.</p>

<p>Because of this placement, a Promoted Trend gets massive exposure and is ideally placed to kickstart or amplify a conversation on Twitter and beyond.</p>

<p>Successful Promoted Trends give users something new and exciting to discover, participate in, and share.</p>

  <img alt="American Express Promoted Trend" class="bordered" src="/a/1314118012/images/business/trends-amex.png" />
<br/>
              <a class="btn btn-m btn-blue" href="../promoted-accounts">Next: Promoted Accounts &rarr;</a>

          </div>
          <div class="five columns" id="contentSecondary">
              <div class="well">
    <h4>Product Snapshot</h4>
    <p>Join some of the world's biggest conversations. Promoted Trends are ideal for:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Building mass awareness</li>
      <li>Product launches and events</li>
      <li>Brand building by association</li>
    </ul>
    <hr />
    <h4>Get Notified</h4>
    <p>Promoted Trends are currently in beta with a small selection of advertisers. Sign up here and get notified when Promoted Trends launches for all advertisers</p>
    <p><a class="btn btn-blue" href="../start">Notify me</a></p>
    <hr />
    <h4>Advertiser Analytics</h4>
    <p>Promoted Trends come with a dedicated Promoted Trends Dashboard, for realtime insight into your campaign's performance.</p>
    <p><a class="btn btn-blue" href="../analytics">Analytics &rarr;</a></p>
